title: This Bert Show Member Conquered Their Biggest Fear Ever
description:
Last week, The Bert Show asked Just Romeo if he noticed any major differences since taking Prozac for anxiety. 
This past weekend he went out of town and had a conversation with a stranger in line and he kept his cool when the flight attendant yelled at him, when before he would’ve been nervous.
